  [Text] Finland will send more peacekeepers to the former 
Yugoslavia. The Defense Ministry reports that a group of 39 
guard soldiers will travel to Pleso near Zagreb, the capital of 
Croatia, in just under a week. The Finns will start guarding 
the Pleso base and airport. So far, the Nordic peacekeepers in 
